\id TIT - Kuna, San Blas - Bible -Panama 2014 (DBL -2014)
\h Tito
\toc1 Titoʼse-Narmaklesad-Garda
\toc2 Tito
\toc3 Tt
\mt1 TITOʼSE-NARMAKLESAD-GARDA
\mt2 TITO
\imt2 GEBE-SOGLENAID
\imt1 Garda-nug
\ip Pablo Macedonia-yargi-gudigu, we-garda Titoʼse narmaksad. Tito, Griego-duled, Pabloʼba Bab-Jesús-abingasgusad. Tito, Pabloʼba Bab-Dummad-Igar-barsogega, bipirmakdii gusad. Pablo, Corinto-neggweburse igar-nudakega, degi, gwenadgan-Jerusalénʼgi-wilemalad-bukmaladga mani-weega, ilabo Tito-barmisgusad. Binsamardo, we-garda birga 62ʼgi narmakles-insaye.
\is1 Titoʼse-Narmaklesad-Gardagi weyob sunmaklenaid
\ip Pablo, Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-danar-ambikunonidamalad-irba e-dummagan-urbega Creta-dupugine Tito-obesgusad. Pablo, Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaledbali, we-gardagi Titoʼga-sogsad, gwenadganga-idumalad-nuegan-urboye. We-gardagi, Titoʼga-sognaid, gwenadgan-idumalad Bab-Igargi-dulemar-odurdakega igi-nanamalargebe.
\ip Pablo, Titoʼga sogbalid be odurdakoye, igi Bab-Dummad-Igargi gwenadgan nanaergebe, degine, igar-napiragwadsulid mer itomaloye.
\ip We-gardagine, weyob ilemakar sunmaklenaid:
\io1 1. Gebe-sikwas-soglenaid (1:1-4).
\io1 2. Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-idumaladga-gued-e-igar (1:5-16).
\io1 3. Igar-nuegan-mamaidgi-odurdakleged (2:1-15).
\io1 4. Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad igi-damalargebe (3:1-11).
\io1 5. Pablo, Titoʼga napi ibmar sogsad (3:12-14).
\io1 6. Napi-soglenaid (3:15).
\ip Be itogua.
\c 1
\ms1 1. GEBE-SIKWAS-SOGLENAID
\mr (1:1-4)
\p 
\v 1 Ani Pablo, Bab-Dummad-e-mai, degine, Jesucristo-e-sapin-bur-dummadga-gumogaga nugsalesbalidid. Dulemar-Bab-Dummadgi-sulearmalad Jesucristoʼgi-bensuli-guegala, degine, Bab-Igar-Maidba igar-napiragwad-wisgumalagala, Bab-Dummad anse gochad.
\v 2 We-dule-sulearmalad bensulidgi burba-geg-bergued edarbedii gumaloed. Ar ade, Bab-Dummad geg-gakansaedi, bato iduar, gebe-negasailaun sogsagusad, burba-geg-bergued ukoye.
\v 3 Bab-Dummad-anmar-Abonoged e-ibagan-nasiksadbali, we-gayaburba anga uknonikid, adi, dulemarga an we-igargi sunmakegar.
\p 
\v 4 Tito, we-garda an bese narmaked. Jesúsʼgi-bensulid be anbo-emar-nikadba be an-machi-sunnadyob gunonikid.
\p Bab-Dummad-anmar-baba, degi, Bab-Jesucristo-anmar-Abonoged, begi nued binsamarsun, degine, wile be-dakbarsun, deginbali, ulubgi bogidik be-itogega imakbarsun.
\ms1 2. JESÚSʼBA-NANAIMALAD-E-IDUMALADGA-GUED-E-IGAR
\mr (1:5-16)
\p 
\v 5 Tito, Creta-dupugi igarmar-besmalad-nudakega an be-obesgusad. Deginbali, an bega sogsagusadyob, neggweburmar-iliba Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-idumalad-urbega an be-obesgusbalid.
\p 
\v 6 Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-idumalad, dule-nued-daed abeleged:
\q2 Dule-egi-ichakwa-sunmaked-sated,
\q2 dule-unnila-ome-wargwenna-nikad,
\q2 e-mimmigan-Bab-Jesúsʼba-nanaid,
\q2 degine, dulemar-geg-e-mimmigangi-sunmakmalad,
\q2 e-mimmigan-uaya-nikaa-damalad.
\p 
\v 7 Ar Jesúsʼba-nanaimalad-e-idumalad-e-dummad, Bab-Dummad-igargi-arbaedsoggu, abeledo:
\q2 Dule-egi-ichakwa-sunmaked-sated,
\q2 dule-na-ebi-ibmar-wisye-na-san-imaksulid,
\q2 dule-itosur-urwesulid,
\q2 dule-geg-mumgued,
\q2 dule-geg-abin-abin-daed-amied,
\q2 dule-geg-ibmar-isganagi-mani-onoged.
\p 
\v 8 Dule bur weyob-daed abeledo:
\q2 Dule-nabir-emar-akwed,
\q2 dule-ibmar-nueganbina-soged,
\q2 dule-binsaed-nikadaed,
\q2 dule-igar-napiragwadbi-imaked,
\q2 dule-gwage-swilidikid,
\q2 dule-nabir-na-san-bargaed.
\p 
\v 9 Deginbali, we-dule, igi Bab-Dummad-Gayaburbagi odurdaklesa, amba deyob e-gwagegi na sediirgebed. Adi, dulemar-baigan-odurdakalir, igar-napiragwadgi e-gwage ogannogegar. Degine, dulemar-igar-nabiridgi-noar-binsadimalad-e-gwage ogwaegar.
\p 
\v 10 Ar amba bukidar Bab-Jesús-Igargi annadimalad, dulemar-yardakdimalad, degi, binsa-ee-sunmakdimalad. We-dulemar bur bule dule-abgan-duku-uka-sikergebe-sogmalad gued.
\v 11 We-dulemar-mer-bar-sunmakega be imakergebed. We-dulemar ibmar-odurdaklegewilubsulid-odurdakedba bela negyagi-bukmalad-oichononidamalad, ibmar-isgana-odurdakedgi mani-onodimalad.
\p 
\v 12 Ar e-dule-wargwen, gayaburba-barsoged, Creta-dupuginmogad, na e-dulemargi sogsagusad:
\q1 “Creta-dupuginmalad, gusgu gadi gakansamalad,
\q2 achu-sapurdamaladyobi damaladid.
\q1 Unnila-mas-gunnedginbi-binsadimaladid,
\q2 degine, wiegala-dulemalad.”
\p 
\v 13 We-dule-ibmar-sogsad ar nue-napira soged. Degisoggu, gatik be amarga gandik ibmar sogo, adi, Jesús-Igargi nued-nanadii gumalagar.
\v 14 Degine, mer binsa Judíoʼmar-nui-sunmakedba damarbaligar, deginbali, dulemar-igar-napiragwadgi-banguddamalad-e-igar-mesedba mer damarbaligar.
\p 
\v 15 Dulemar-gwage-nuegangardi, ibmar-belagwapa swilidik naid. Ar dulemar-gwage-sunnasur-gudimaladgardi, Bab-Jesús-bengudimaladgardi, belagwapa ibmar isgusadbi naid. Ar ade, a-dulemarga e-binsaedse-bakale, e-ulubgi-ibmar-itogedse-bakale, bato isgus naid.
\v 16 Ar Bab-Dummad-wisye sogmalando, ar na e-damaladgindi, Bab-Dummad-osulodimalad. A-dulemar ibmar-isgana imakmalad, Bab-Dummad-sogedba ibmar-imaksurmaladsoggu, bela ibmar-nuegan-imakleged geg imakmarsundo.
\c 2
\ms1 3. IGAR-NUEGAN-MAMAIDGI-ODURDAKLEGED
\mr (2:1-15)
\p 
\v 1 Tito, ar bedi Jesús-Igar-nuegan-mamaidba be innikii sunmako.
\p 
\v 2 Dadormarga be sogo:
\q2 Mer dogdar wilub-obichaa damaloye,
\q2 mer dodoakwaa damaloye,
\q2 nue-binsaed-nikaa damaloye,
\q2 Jesúsʼgi-nue-bensuli gumaloye,
\q2 nue sabgumaloye,
\q2 degine, mer ukurmakar ibmar abemaloye.
\p 
\v 3 Amba deyob mukwamarga be sogmogoed:
\q2 E-daedgi Bab-Dummad-dobee nanamaloye,
\q2 mer dule-baigan-ogakansamaloye,
\q2 mer mumgudii nanamaloye,
\q2 ibmar-nueganginbi dulemar-baigan-odurdakdii nanamaloye.
\p 
\v 4 Deginbali, mukwamarga be sogbalo, omegan-odurdakbaloye:
\q2 E-nusgana-sabguedgi,
\q2 e-suimar-sabguedgi,
\q2 
\v 5 nue-binsaed-nikadaedgi,
\q2 san-swilidik-nanaedgi,
\q2 neg-nued-akwedgi,
\q2 nueddaedgi,
\q2 e-sui-urbaligwa-nanaedgi,
\q3 adi, dulemar mer Bab-Dummad-Gayaburbagi isdar sunmakmalagarye.
\p 
\v 6 Deginbali, sapingana be weyob unabalo:
\q2 Nue-binsaed-nikaa damaloye.
\p 
\v 7 Tito, bedi be bela ibmar-nuegan-saedgi sapinganga be oyogoed, igi nanamalargebe.
\q2 Ulubgi akar-binsasulidgi,
\q2 degi, sunmaked-napiragwadgi dodoakwaadasulidgi,
\q3 be sapingan-odurdakoed.
\p 
\v 8 Gaya-nuegangi be sunmakoed. We-gayagi dule geg akar soged. Weyob be odurdakele, be-isdarmalad be obingegsaoed. Ar ade, begi ibmar-isdarmalad geg soge-gumaloed.
\p 
\v 9 Maigan be weyob ounabalo:
\q2 Be-dummagan-ibmar-sogedba be damarye,
\q2 bela yeer-itoged be imakye,
\q2 melle abin be sunmakmarye.
\q2 
\v 10 Degine, mer e-ibe be ibmar atursamaloye.
\q2 Na be oyoged imakmarye, bemar geg-dulemar-yardakmaladye,
\q3 adi, begi dakmalagar, Bab-Dummad-anmar-Abonoged-e-Igar, igar-nuedi.
\p 
\v 11 Bab-Dummad bela nabir dulemargi binsamaid. Ar Bab-Dummad nabir dulemargi binsaewilubsulinad. Emigindi, isguedgi bela dulemar-abonogega, e-nabir-binsaed bela dulemarga oyononikid.
\p 
\v 12 Bab-Dummad nabir-anmargi-binsaedba we-igarmargi anmar-odurdaknonikid:
\q2 Bab-Dummadgi-binsasuli-nanaed-obaned,
\q2 ibmar-isganagi-binsaed-obaned.
\p Adi,
\q2 weyobi anmar we-napneg-naidgi nue-binsaed-nikaa nanaegar,
\q2 ibmar-innikigwadbi-imakdii guegar,
\q2 nue-Bab-Dummad-dobee-nanadii guegar.
\p 
\v 13 Emide anmar, bensulidgi anmar-Bab-Jesucristo-Abonoged-nuedid e-gangued-yeerdaklegedgi-gannar-danikoed edarbedimarsunnad.
\p 
\v 14 We-Jesucristoʼde isguedgi anmar-onogegala, anmar-anar na san-burba uksagusad, anmar-anar burgwisad. Adi, bela anmar-isgudiid eliega, egadga anmar-imakega swilidik anmar-imaksad. Adi, anmar ibmar-nueganbi imakdii guegar.
\p 
\v 15 Tito, weyob bega ibmar-soglesadba be sunmako, be dule-unao, gandikidba weyob be ibmar sogo. Mer dulemar ibgwensur-be-daked be imako.
\c 3
\ms1 4. JESÚSʼBA-NANAIMALAD IGI-DAMALARGEBE
\mr (3:1-11)
\p 
\v 1 Tito, gwenadganga gannar be sogo, insamaloye:
\q2 Dule-negsemamaid-urbaligwa be nanamaloye,
\q2 dummagan-mamaid-urbaligwa be nanamaloye,
\q2 amar-sogedba damaloye.
\q2 Ibmar-nueganbi-imakegala, be guagwar gudii gumaloye.
\q2 
\v 2 Mer dulemargi ichakwa sunmakmaloye,
\q3 bur be bogidik gudiguo.
\q2 Bur dulemargi binsaed-nikaa damaloye,
\q2 bela dulemar-baigan-urbaligwadaed na be imakmaloye.
\p 
\v 3 Ar anmar epenne deyob binsaedsuli-gudii gusmogad, Bab-Dummadba ibmar-imaksuli-gudii gusmogad. Weyob anmar gudii gusad:
\q2 Yardakles-gudii,
\q2 ibmar-isgana-maiga-gudii,
\q2 ibmar-isganagi-wergudii,
\q2 ibmar-isganagi-binsadii,
\q2 nobgudii,
\q2 dulemarse-isdar-dakledii,
\q2 degine, muchub-muchub-na-isdar-dakdii,
\q3 anmar gusmalad.
\p 
\v 4 Ar Bab-Dummad-anmar-Abonoged-e-nued-dulemargi-binsaed-oyolenonigu, degine, bela e-sabgued dulemarse-oyolenonigu,
\v 5 Bab Dummad wile-anmar-daksadba anmar-abonononikid. Anmar ibmar-innikii-imaksadbarsulid. Bab-Dummad-Burba-Isligwaled-uksadba anmarga isgued-elinonikid, burba-dulad anmarga uknonikid. Deyob anmar-abonononikid.
\v 6 Anmar-Abonoged-Jesucristoʼba, Bab-Dummad anmarga E-Burba-Isligwaled unnitiba uknonikid.
\v 7 Bab-Dummad anmargi-nabir-binsamaidba, isgussuliyob anmar-daknonikid, degine, bensulidgi burba-geg-bergued-edarbediguega anmar-imaksad.
\p 
\v 8 Tito, we-Gayaburba, napiragwadid. We-Gayaburbagi nue-gandikidba dule-odurdaknai an be-abeged, adi, dulemar-Bab-Dummad-bensurmalad ibmar-nueganbi imakdigumalagar. We-ibmarmar, ibmar-nueganad, degine, dulemarga ibmar-nueganga gubalid.
\p 
\v 9 Ar ibmargi-binsa-ee-sunmaklemaladgi, dadgan-danimalad-igargi, mer be sunmakdii guo. Muchub-muchub-abin-abin-imakmaladgi, Moisés-Igar-Mesisadgi-abin-abin-urwemaladgi, mer be sunmakdii guo.
\p Ar weyob sunmaklegedi, binsaledid, gwen ibmar-nueganga gusulid.
\p 
\v 10 Ar dule-wargwen sordamar-mamardiile, ese be goloed. Irbo-goledgi be-itosulile, a-dule be onogoed.
\v 11 Ar be wisid, we-dule-degidaedi, isgudiid, galagwensuli gudiid. Ar na e-daedbali, bato odurdakleged-igar ega megisdo.
\ms1 5. PABLO, TITOʼGA NAPI IBMAR SOGSAD
\mr (3:12-14)
\p 
\v 12 Artemas an bese barmidodibe, Tíquicoʼdibe. We-gwensak bese-modapile, be gwae anse Nicópolis-neggweburse-daged imako. Ar a-neggweburgi an dii-wied-niigi mai guoed.
\v 13 Dule-irwa-gwisgued-Zenas, degine, Apolos, amarga ibmar be ukmalo, adi, neggwebur-baidsik-nadmalar, melle ibmar-sate igarba nadapi gumalagar.
\v 14 Degine, anmar-sordamarmoga, ibmar-nuegan-imaked durdakmarmogoed, adi, dule-ibmarsurmaladga ibmar-nuegan-imakega, mer binsa Bab-Jesúsʼba nanadii gumalagar.
\ms1 6. NAPI-SOGLENAID
\mr (3:15)
\p 
\v 15 Bela an-walik-bukmalad bega sogsimardo, bemarde nued sogeye. Dulemar-Jesúsʼgi-bensurmalad-anmar-sabmaladga be sogo, bemar nued sogeye.
\p Bab-Dummad nued bemargi binsasun.
